      <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
        Molded studs for dry natural grass pitches and universal use.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌧️</div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Soft Ground (SG)</h3>
